# Value of an average passenger flight {#sec-value-of-an-average-passenger-flight}

## EUROCONTROL recommended values

This value represents the monetised benefits of an average passenger flight in
the EU27.^[[EU27 in 2013](https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/statistics-explained/index.php/Glossary:EU_enlargements)]
The values were adjusted to 2022 price levels from 2013 based on inflation.


